data.description: This beautiful Spanish style exterior home welcomes you to the sought-after Mesquite Grove Estates neighborhood. As you enter through a custom gated wrought iron entry into your private paved courtyard, you are welcomed into this elegantly designed home with spacious split-floor plan offering ton of natural light through large windows throughout. The lovely foyer entry welcomes you into the designed-for-entertaining formal living room with soaring ceilings, carpet and tile in all the right places. Make your way to a breathtaking large airy dine-in kitchen intrigued with ample kitchen cabinet space that is surrounded by gorgeous bullnose edge granite countertops, coupled with Stainless Steel appliances and gas stovetop along with a large breakfast island bar. Stay seamlessly connected as you host parties/get-togethers with an open family room with a built-in TV wall niche. As you retreat to the master Suite, enjoy the roomy bathroom with double sinks, separate glass shower & tub and a large walk-in closet. As you complete your day, sit back and relax in your beautifully landscaped backyard featuring a sparkling pool with refinished pool decking and water/rock feature. Maintain all your seasonal fun and toys in this split 3-Car Garage. Located in the Chandler Unified School District, just minutes away from Chandler Museum and Crayola Experience Chandler. Close to Chandler Fashion Center, Restaurants/Shopping, GOLF, Loop 202, Mesa Gateway Airport & Arizona State University.
